@startuml Facility_Reservation
title Facility & Reservation - Use Case Diagram
top to bottom direction
skinparam nodesep 50
skinparam ranksep 60
skinparam shadowing false

actor Investor
actor Guardian
actor "Facility Manager" as FM

rectangle "Facility & Reservation" {
  usecase "Browse Facilities" as UC11
  usecase "View Facility Details" as UC12
  usecase "Reserve Facility" as UC13
  usecase "Cancel Reservation" as UC14
  usecase "Make Payment" as UC18
  usecase "Send Notification" as UC25
}

Investor --> UC11
Investor --> UC12
Investor --> UC13
Investor --> UC14
FM --> UC12

UC13 ..> UC18 : <<include>>
UC25 ..> UC13 : <<extend>>
UC25 ..> UC14 : <<extend>>

note right of UC18
  Make Payment is defined in the
  Payments subsystem (05_payments.puml).
end note
note right of UC25
  Send Notification is triggered
  by the Notification Service actor
  (see 06_communication.puml).
end note

@enduml
